comment: LHH shows Harden (HOU) makes contact with Walker's (CHA) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.

Harden (HOU) extends his arm into Williams (CHA), affecting his ability to defend the shot attempt.

Williams (CHA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Harden (HOU) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Harrell (HOU) maintains legal guarding position on the jump shot attempt by Kaminsky (CHA) and any contact is incidental.
Harden (HOU) and Williams (CHA) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.

Belinelli (CHA) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
